                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d120">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Jernigan</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Denby.</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-08-27">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">August</hi> 27, 1894</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Cable Gresham asylum only granted. Suspected have resided here three years as
                    students. Are boys. Papers in their possession such as intelligent students
                    might prepare for personal information. Suggest American consuls act as
                    arbitrators.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Jernigan.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
